summary: I learned Spider-Man almost joined the Avengers twice in its initial lineup's days in 1963. Since the Avengers were SUPPOSED to...
question: I learned Spider-Man almost joined the Avengers twice in its initial lineup's days in 1963. Since the Avengers were SUPPOSED to be Marvel's biggest "solo" heroes teaming up a la the Justice League, how would a '63 Spidey membership and perhaps Hulk remaining with the team affect them in both a meta sense AND storytelling opportunities, as well as how it'd affect Spidey and Hulk themselves? For the sake of things, say everyone still leaves to allow the "Cap's Kooky Quartet" era to occur on time.
answer: Never happen - in-universe they were the big guns, but out of it they were the also-rans being grouped together. Spidey was too big for them.

unless loki and Stephen have anything to say about it
body:
Welcome back to ‘Thoughts with BlitzyBear’

Omega superhero Tony Stark is on the run after a villain that he has been chasing after for years now finds out that he is an omega and was using suppressants. He is trying his damn hardest to not be tracked down but after a couple of days of hide and seek, he comes to the realization that the stupid wizard is toying with him. I mean the idiot did tell Tony that they were going to be mated. That was the whole reason why he was on the run in the first place.

Alpha villain Stephen dark mother fuckin sorcerer Strange has know Tony longer than Tony thinks. Well he did until the day he finds out that Tony who has been acting like he is king of the world missed taking his meds and went into heat during a battle between the two. He goes on the hunt and decides to not use too much of his magic. He likes the chase and thinks the payoff will totally be worth it. After all…..he has decided that he is going to be Tony’s mate.

… _ _ _ …

One day Stephen gets the help of Alpha Loki to try and take over New York.

The attack with the help of The Chitauri goes forth.

During the battle Loki lays eyes on the omega Stephen was talking about and instantly wants him.

He tells Stephen and a fight between the two commence.

While the two fight, the Avengers take this advantage to destroy the Chitauri.

The fight between Stephen and Loki come to a hault half an hour later when Loki hears Thor yell at Tony to “get back here Stark right now!”.

The two watch in concern as Tony who has a hold of a rocket is flown in to the sky. The yell out Tony’s name as the portal in the sky close.

5 minutes later is nothing but silence.

Sigh of relief sets in when they see Tony coming back down. That relief is short lived as they race towards Tony who isn’t slowing down.

Stephen and Loki are almost there but stop as Thor zooms past them and catch Tony before landing back on the ground.

Loki and Stephen race towards the Avengers, everyone wondering if Tony is going to be ok.

Much to everyones relief and with the shout of the Hulk, Tony wakes up and starts joking around asking if someone kissed him.

Thor takes this opportunity to rip the iron Man suit off of Tony and kiss him with so much fear, so much passion that neither want to let go.

Loki and Stephen choke at what is happening infront of them.

The Avengers smile at their favorite couple

blog.name: whatamicryingovershoulders
blog.title: All the Awful Fanfics You Could Dream Of
blog.description: I’m going to be so bad at this, BUT! Hi, call me hoe because I am one and love to write fanfics. If you actually like my writing (which I’d never understand why) and have a request, drown me in them....please.

body:
Apple bottom jeans

(How does one fill this out?)

Characters: Y/N, Steve Rogers, Natasha Romanoff, mention of Tony

Pairing: Steve x Reader (idk if you would call it a pairing but skeet)

Word count: I don’t got a fucking clue

Summary: On a way to a dinner hosted by Tony, you jam to Apple bottom jeans while Steve drives

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

When Natasha had suggested that Steve wouldn’t want to ride with you, he grew confused. Tony was hosting a dinner as usual, one to include fancy food, jostling music, and a sleek building. You, of course, were delighted to attend such dinners. The thought of dressing up in a gown quickly to your interest. It was the night to feel as if you were a goddess.

“Why shouldn’t she ride with me?” Slender fingers drummed a top dainty countertops as Steve prodded his friend, brows drawing together with none other than confusion. Nat had only offered a hesitant smile.

“She’ll beg for the aux,” she informed, painted nails chipping as she picked at them with growing boredom. Adjusting herself upon a metal stool, she began demolishing petite sugar packages.

“So?”

“So,” Nat drawled out, single brow perking as green eyes peered from lashes. “You’ll nonstop have to listen to her music. I love that girl, but.” A slight pause as she glanced around. “Her music taste isn’t that great.”

Steve merely brushed off the suggestion. He’ll drive (y/n) if he wanted to. It was 7:36P.M. when it came to conclusion that Nat was right. Unwillingly to admit, he allowed (y/n) to listen as she please. He found it quite amusing on another hand.

“SHAWTY HAD THEM APPLE BOTTOM JEANS, BOOTS WITH THE FUR!” You belted, arms stretching to flail childishly to the beat. Steve cackled loudly, attention from the road dwindling.

“NEXT THING YA KNOW.” And alas, if Steve had kept track of everytime he laughed so viciously, this would have been number one. Your hand grasped a hiding handle, pulling the lever until your seat did as told. And with each beat, you pushed your seat back.

“SHAWTY GOT LOW, LOW, LOW, LOW!”

You, of course, were delighted to attend such dinners. The thought of dressing up in a gown quickly to your interest. It was the night to feel as if you were a goddess.

“Why shouldn’t she ride with me?” Slender fingers drummed a top dainty countertops as Steve prodded his friend, brows drawing together with none other than confusion. Nat had only offered a hesitant smile.

“She’ll beg for the aux,” she informed, painted nails chipping as she picked at them with growing boredom. Adjusting herself upon a metal stool, she began demolishing petite sugar packages.

“So?”

“So,” Nat drawled out, single brow perking as green eyes peered from lashes. “You’ll nonstop have to listen to her music. I love that girl, but.” A slight pause as she glanced around. “Her music taste isn’t that great.”

body:
285 days until Avengers 4!

229 days until Captain Marvel!!

it’s like 3:30 am bc i fell asleep in the middle of the day and slept all the way til like midnight so now i can’t sleep anymore. i decided to do this before i forget again bc i haven’t had a lot of time to make these recently so i would like to apologize for that hhhhhhh i missed a lot of days i’m sorry.

anyway. idk if any of you guys saw the hydralogs au thing on twitter but for like three days that was all i’ve been doing lmao. god that shit got intense my group chat for it was flooding as well lmao. it’s over now, but it was one of the best interactive aus i’ve done holy shit the mods were so good (i dmed the original creator and almost got to be a loki account but then changed my mind bc we couldn’t figure out a way to make it fit into the story lmao. i was fine with being a player though, so it was chill lmao)

moving on, this might be pretty long bc i’m bored and need to make up for all the days i missed so bear with me lmao. my orchestra summer camp starts on monday and hhhhhh i only got like 3 days to practice my pieces bc i just got bad from vacation a few days ago. i’m gonna flop the entire thing but you know what fuck it. god i have my school’s band camp soon too agGhH juST GiVe mE SOmE tiMe JEysUS

OH AND ALSO!! I’M GOING TO INTERACTIVE INTROVERTS TOMORROW! (well, today, but it’s still night so i’m gonna say tomorrow bc i’m a bad bitch you can’t tell me what to do) IT’S AT 7 PM IN PITTSBURGH AAAAHHH. AND THE THING IS IT’S AT THE EXACT SAME THEATER AS WHERE I SAW MARKIPLIER AT LAST YEAR. BUT BITCH I’M GONNA BE BREATHING THE SAME AIR AS DAN AND PHIL IN 16 HOURS

speaking of interactive introverts, i saw an ad for it in manila lol

i also saw a giant ass poster of seventeen there. i cant remember if i already mention that here before.

anyway mayhaps i should try to go back to sleep. that’s probably a good idea right. ok welp. goodnight(?)
